            <note xml:id="foot.f2">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-12520.xml">letter to James Torbitt, 6 March 1880</ref>. The letter from <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_788.xml">James Caird</ref> to <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1599.xml">Thomas Henry Farrer</ref> has not been found in the Darwin Archive–CUL.</note>
